spell_list.description: The Summoner is granted control of their pet, including movement, attack and using spells through the perspective of their pet. Your pet also gains Empower Servant, which instantly replenishes some of the power of any ability used. Some of that power is converted into a heal for your pet. This ability grants 4 intelligence and stamina passively per rank as well.
